---

<ChapterShell chapterId="02" locale="en">
  <div slot="thesis">
    <p lang="zh-CN">
      （正文仍以中文源稿为准）当一次 Tool 调用既改变世界又产生巨量输出时，如何留下「发生过什么」的证据，同时不拖垮同一
      Turn 的下一次推理？
    </p>
  </div>

  <Section
    id="keystone"
    label="§02 · Keystone"
    title="Turn-level evidence pipeline"
    lede="Scene-local metaphor; the fixed system is NewsLiquid tokens, hand keystones, and motion discipline."
  >
    <DiagramFigure
      prototype
      caption="Fig. 1 · A Tool Result splits into four representations; active prune rewrites Provider messages only — never Evidence."
      alt="Pipeline from Tool execution to Runtime Event, Artifact, Turn Evidence, then Provider messages; 01–04 persist as evidence; 05 may be pruned; invariant: Prune the context, never prune the evidence."
    >
      <EvidencePipelineKeystone />
    </DiagramFigure>

    <p class="figure-note">
      Invariant: <strong>Prune the context, never prune the evidence.</strong>
      Pipeline metaphor is local to §02.
    </p>
  </Section>
</ChapterShell>

